### Azure API Management AI Gateway - API 테스트
### VS Code REST Client 확장 필요
### https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

@apimUrl = https://<apim-name>.azure-api.net
@subscriptionKey = <your-subscription-key>
@apiVersion = 2025-04-01-preview
@deploymentName = gpt-4.1-nano

###############################################################################
# Lab 2: 기본 호출 테스트
###############################################################################

### 2-1. Health Check
GET {{apimUrl}}/status-0123456789abcdef

### 2-2. 기본 Chat Completion
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [
        {"role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "안녕하세요! 간단히 인사해주세요."}
    ],
    "max_tokens": 50,
    "temperature": 0.7
}

### 2-3. 잘못된 Subscription Key (401 기대)
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: invalid-key-12345

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "test"}],
    "max_tokens": 5
}

### 2-4. Subscription Key 없이 호출 (401 기대)
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "test"}],
    "max_tokens": 5
}

###############################################################################
# Lab 3: 로드밸런싱 테스트
# → 여러 번 호출하여 x-backend-url 응답 헤더를 확인하세요
#   3개 백엔드(eastus, swedencentral, westus)로 분산되어야 합니다
###############################################################################

### 3-1. 로드밸런싱 호출 #1 → 응답의 x-backend-url 헤더 확인
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Which backend am I on? Reply in 3 words."}],
    "max_tokens": 10
}

### 3-2. 로드밸런싱 호출 #2
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Which backend am I on? Reply in 3 words."}],
    "max_tokens": 10
}

### 3-3. 로드밸런싱 호출 #3
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Which backend am I on? Reply in 3 words."}],
    "max_tokens": 10
}

### 3-4. 로드밸런싱 호출 #4
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Which backend am I on? Reply in 3 words."}],
    "max_tokens": 10
}

###############################################################################
# Lab 4: 정책 테스트
###############################################################################

### 4-1. 토큰 Rate Limiting 테스트 (큰 토큰으로 호출, 반복하면 429 기대)
# → 응답 헤더의 x-ratelimit-remaining-tokens 값 변화 확인
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Write a detailed essay about cloud computing."}],
    "max_tokens": 2000
}

### 4-2. 캐싱 테스트 - 1차 호출 (캐시 미스, 느림)
# → 응답 시간 기록
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of South Korea?"}],
    "max_tokens": 20
}

### 4-3. 캐싱 테스트 - 2차 호출 (캐시 히트, 빠름)
# → 동일 프롬프트, 응답 시간 비교
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of South Korea?"}],
    "max_tokens": 20
}

### 4-4. 캐싱 테스트 - 유사 프롬프트 (시맨틱 캐시 히트?)
# → 의미가 같지만 표현이 다른 질문
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Tell me the capital city of Korea"}],
    "max_tokens": 20
}

###############################################################################
# Lab 5: Gemini 로드밸런싱 테스트 (네이티브 포맷)
###############################################################################

### 5-1. Gemini 단일 호출
POST {{apimUrl}}/gemini/models/gemini-2.5-flash-lite:generateContent
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "contents": [{"role": "user", "parts": [{"text": "Which AI model are you? Reply in one line."}]}],
    "generationConfig": {"maxOutputTokens": 30}
}

### 5-2. Gemini 호출 #2 (로드밸런싱 확인 — 반복 실행)
POST {{apimUrl}}/gemini/models/gemini-2.5-flash-lite:generateContent
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "contents": [{"role": "user", "parts": [{"text": "Say hello in Korean."}]}],
    "generationConfig": {"maxOutputTokens": 30}
}

### 5-3. Gemini 호출 #3 (로드밸런싱 확인 — 반복 실행)
POST {{apimUrl}}/gemini/models/gemini-2.5-flash-lite:generateContent
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "contents": [{"role": "user", "parts": [{"text": "What is 1+1?"}]}],
    "generationConfig": {"maxOutputTokens": 10}
}

###############################################################################
# Lab 7: 고급 패턴 테스트
###############################################################################

### 7-1. SSE 스트리밍 응답
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Count from 1 to 5, one per line."}],
    "max_tokens": 50,
    "stream": true
}

### 7-2. 큰 프롬프트 + 작은 max_tokens (토큰 사용량 확인용)
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [
        {"role": "system", "content": "You are a concise assistant. Maximum 1 sentence."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "서울의 인구는 몇 명인가요?"}
    ],
    "max_tokens": 30
}

### 7-3. IP 제한 테스트 (ip-filter 정책 적용 후)
# → IP 차단 정책 적용 시 403 기대
POST {{apimUrl}}/openai/deployments/{{deploymentName}}/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

{
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Am I blocked?"}],
    "max_tokens": 10
}
